{"tid":1581400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有間畫室話要比你哋大大力懲罰","createTime":"2019-09-19T14:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T15:43:33.000Z","uid":37924,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c22c38a4fbfb3a06a6af12598dc1beee41a6c667","tid":1581400,"uid":37924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oVt8cNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoVt8cNU.jpg&h=a23bed3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我哋係一班來自民間嘅畫家<br />\n知道呢幾個月好多人放棄咗自己日常生活入面嘅興趣投入社運<br />\n無論身體同心理都飽受煎熬<br />\n除左文字，用手用筆用顏料都係一條可以抒發平伏情緒同表達嘅渠道<br />\n希望大家可以狠狠地用你哋腦海入面嘅畫面懲罰我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩唔開心，等我哋和你傾，和你畫，和你減壓，和大家一起過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有野飲，有飯食，有涼沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生證免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n非學生兩小時 $50 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/heyarthk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fheyarthk&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=259ea7ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/heyarthk</a>"},{"pid":"deedffe88e5d3aa6904692f54f5c7a2762762e10","tid":1581400,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\